Component Needed:
1. Arduino Board (Uno)
2. Dabble App (installed on smartphone)
3. Bluetooth Module (HC-05, HC-06, or Dabble-supported module)
4. Adafruit Motor Shield (compatible with AFMotor library)
5. 2 × DC Motors
6. 2 × Wheels
7. Robot Chassis
8. Battery Pack (suitable for Arduino and motors)
9. Jumper Wires
10. Smartphone (for Dabble app control)

Optional:
1 × Caster Wheel
Switch (for power control)
Screws, Nuts, and Mounting Hardware



🛠️ Arduino Library Installation Guide
📦 Libraries to Install in Arduino IDE

Open Arduino IDE
Go to Sketch > Include Library > Manage Libraries…

🔍 Search and Install the Following Libraries:
✅ 1. Dabble
Search: Dabble
Author: STEMpedia
Click: Install

✅ 2. AFMotor
Search: Adafruit Motor Shield or AFMotor
Author: Adafruit
Click: Install
